2.0.1
  * Test the validity of options values early in the script execution to throw
  an error before any potentially long task
  * Fix some debug messages
  * Print 'OK' on potentially long tasks completion without a visual
  progression indicator
  * If lsb_release is not available and no package format has been explictly
  set, display a warning before falling back on 'deb' format
  * On Debian >= 9 (Stretch), installation instructions show apt usage instead
  of dpkg + apt-get
